CTU  FEE  Admissions  Study programmes conducted in English



Study programmes conducted in English
We offer following programmes taught in English:
Bachelor's degree programmes
It takes three years to earn a Bachelor of Science (B.Sc.) degree.


Electrical Engineering and Computer Science


The standard period of studies in bachelor programs is 6 semesters (3 years).
Master's degree programmes
After completing bachelor's program, it takes two years to earn Master of Science (MSc) program.


Electrical Engineering, Power Engineering and Management

Electronics and Communications

Cybernetics and Robotics

Open Informatics


Aerospace Engineering


The standard period of studies in master programs is 4 semesters (2 years).
Doctoral degree programme
Students who wish to continue their studies towards Ph.D. in doctoral degree programme can choose from 16 fields of specialization.



				Responsible person: 
				doc. Ing. Jiří Jakovenko, Ph.D.







